{"tid":969713,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打比拿拿MOVE嘅司機威脅過?","createTime":"2019-01-05T09:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T03:36:27.000Z","uid":64156,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f8dc01580536c0fcf47d8ebaef6b07fc079bf0e1","tid":969713,"uid":64156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T09:12:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n話說我向一間網購公司做野<br />\n咁平時多單得滯 我地會叫拿拿MOVE司機接單送貨比客<br />\n<br />\n點知早排遇到個司機接左我地張單<br />\n竟然夾單送左第二D貨先 <br />\n比我發現左<br />\n咁我地D野食要新鮮送架嘛 <br />\n話佢 點知佢爆粗屌鳩我 (用voice message)<br />\n<br />\n咁我興興地咪去拿拿MOVE投訴 (有voice message做證)<br />\n<br />\n跟住早兩日佢打黎鬧話我地搞到佢比拿拿MOVE炒左 冇左份工<br />\n要我地同拿拿MOVE取消投訴...<br />\n<br />\n咁老闆見人地冇左份工咁慘 都同意我取消投訴<br />\n點知拿拿MOVE唔肯取消 唔肯跟進<br />\n<br />\n然後個司機再屌鳩我 話唔賠償佢生計嘅話<br />\n要黎公司門口伏我 去食環署唱我地食物中毒<br />\n結果尋日食環真係上黎CHECK公司<br />\n話我地D野食到人地個仔肚痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n忙左兩日 搞到自己 搞到公司 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4838ad0c6a4dc64aac9849df876b5522ecf08761","tid":969713,"uid":3932,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T09:16:18.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正 驚咩"},{"pid":"8beac9c6f3f5a49696222f4debab96c34e8d42f3","tid":969713,"uid":60048,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T09:16:34.000Z","msg":"開司機名<br />\n繼續玩大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e1452fcbb2cae0189e9e3983584e87264966f5","tid":969713,"uid":201158,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T09:18:58.000Z","msg":"有voice  message 報警囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362e45156eb0ffc7f96a59bf65912bbc6768b4d2","tid":969713,"uid":37107,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T09:19:57.000Z","msg":"開司機名啦"},{"pid":"b03fc472ccfd0d27bdea05109b81237e5e917446","tid":969713,"uid":64156,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"8beac9c6f3f5a49696222f4debab96c34e8d42f3","tid":969713,"uid":60048,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T09:16:34.000Z","msg":"開司機名<br />\n繼續玩大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T09:21:07.000Z","m